{"tid":2330533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旅行社疑誇大員工人數呃防疫津貼　警拘62人涉串謀詐騙","createTime":"2020-12-18T05:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T06:12:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"56c77460b929b52506c2b64387ad3dc141beac34","tid":2330533,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"中國肺炎疫情肆虐，嚴重打擊本港旅行業，政府4月曾推出防疫抗疫基金2.0旅遊業支援計劃，向旅行代理商發放一筆過2萬元至20萬元不等的津貼。但有不法商人卻窺準機會，刻意誇大實際員工人數，意圖騙取更多津貼。警方經調查後，以「串謀詐騙」拘捕62人，今日下午2時將於警察總部召開記者會交代案情。"},{"pid":"14c5b82d0187ad989059a8a99a2dca5d377cf7c4","tid":2330533,"uid":111909,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"狂賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83573517cfe2ee63d5c7c6f6a3067b5cec36c48","tid":2330533,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2edf4e07d54ef666f47953882ee7171064a489","tid":2330533,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"又選擇性執法<br />\n後台勁就冇事"},{"pid":"754d79ddf5d69ce4d8fc4ed2233315acd92bea60","tid":2330533,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a864089011efa8178b42d12bbd0ec028050aefc8","tid":2330533,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e2edf4e07d54ef666f47953882ee7171064a489","tid":2330533,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"又選擇性執法<br />\n後台勁就冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"又選擇性執法<br />\n咁多違泊唔抄 淨係抄我"},{"pid":"f352be8fa90de43c1a33ac55889aa37aaf979c0a","tid":2330533,"uid":380218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-